Package com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClearPolicy
    Used to determine when FAST dictionaries are cleared.
    IFastContext
    An instance of this interface encapsulates the context in which FAST encoding and decoding takes place.
    IFastContextFactory
    Creates IFastContext's which can be used to drive the encoding and decoding of FAST messages according to a given set of FAST rules (templates).
    ISpy
    Object which can track internal processing for debugging and display purposes.
    ITemplateSelector
    Interface for classes which contain the logic for selecting which template should be used to encode a given message.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstantMessageTypeTemplateSelector
    Template selector which attempts to select a template from a given ITemplates object based on the value of the message field associated with a particular field tag number - the selector tag number.
    Constants  
    FastBytesDecoder
    Provides simple byte[] interface to decoding process.
    FastDecoder
    CameronFAST utility for decoding any FAST input stream.
    FastEncoder
    CameronFAST utility for encoding messages using FAST.
    FastEncoderDecoder  
    FastInputStream
    Input stream used to receive and decode FAST messages.
    FastOutputStream
    Output stream used to encode and send FAST messages.
    FastTagOrderingRegistry
    Generates tag ordering information given FAST templates.
    SampleFastCompatibleMessage
    Very simple implementation of a message which can be encoded and decoded using our FAST libraries.
    Spy  
    StandardClearPolicy
    Standard implementation of IClearPolicy.
    StandardFastContext  
    TemplateTagSelector
    Template selector which selects templates based on the templateID found in the message field with a particular tag number.
